nodes.text: Blanco was a perky female of unidentified species. She was seen in Depatar, the City of Masks, in 31 BBY. Like all the visitors and many inhabitants, this person was in disguise, particularly in a white-and-silver gown, with web silver covering it. She was seen dancing in Club 111 in a fast style, equivalent to her conversation style.
